                <h5>How long does it take until I see my gear for sale on Out&amp;Back's website?</h5>
                <div class="row">
                    <p class="col-md-12">We focus on important details like thorough cleaning and repair before any gear is available for sale. Depending on the condition of the gear, such processes can take up to 2 weeks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

